<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googlepis.com">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <title>order confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body{
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4ff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container{
            max-width: 600px;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #4f5ef1;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .message{
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }
        .messsage-sm{
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }
        .messsage-sm > h1{
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .course-info{
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px 0px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(206, 197,197, 0.1);
            color: #000;
    
        }
        .course-info > h4{
            color: #23bd70;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-family: "poppins", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 !important;
            margin-top: 0 !important;
        }
        .course-name{
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .purchase-info{
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .total{
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer{
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .footer > p >a{
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .flex{
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #9999993f;
        }
        .flex h4{
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .flex.lg{
            width: 85%;
            margin: auto;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .first-td{
            font-weight: 600 !important;
        }
        .seciond-td{
            font-weight: 500 !important;
            color: #0000006f;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .title{
            font-size: 16px !important;
        }
        table{
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
    
        td{
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 28.33%;
        }
        td.col-2{
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .m-auto{
            width: 100%;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .table-row{
            width: 70%;
            display: block;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="messsage-sm">
            <h1>Your E learning order is confirmed!</h1>
            <p>And we're just as exited as you are.</p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>
        <div class="course-info">
            <h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        order #: <%= order._id %>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        order Date: <%= order.date %>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table>
                <tr style="width: 90%; margin:auto; display: block;">
                    <td class="first-td">Item</td>
                    <td class="first-td">Qty</td>
                    <td class="first-td">cost</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table style="width: 90%; margin:auto; display: block;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="seciond-td"><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td class="seciond-td">1</td>
                    <td class="seciond-td">$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <table class="table-row" style="border-top: 1px solid #00000029;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-2">Subtotal:</td>
                    <td class="col-2"><%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>

            </table>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-2">Total:</td>
                    <td class="col-2"><%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any question, plese contact our support team at 
                <a href="mailto:subhamkundu.bankura@gmail.com">subhamkundu.bankura12@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Elearning, All rights recived.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>